{"id":12,"parent_id":2,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":12,"title":"Matthew 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"Matt.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus instructs and empowers the Twelve Apostles and sends them forth to preach, minister, and heal the sick—Those who receive the Twelve receive the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.1","order":"03.03.010.1248"},["b","1"],"And when he had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"called"],"unto",["i","him"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"twelve disciples"],", he gave them",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"power",["i","against"]],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"unclean spirits"],", to cast them out, and to",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_1e"},"heal"],"all manner of",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_1f"},"sickness"],"and all manner of disease."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.2","order":"03.03.010.1249"},["b","2"],"Now the names of the twelve apostles are these; The first, Simon, who is called Peter, and Andrew his brother; James",["i","the son"],"of Zebedee, and John his brother;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.3","order":"03.03.010.1250"},["b","3"],"Philip, and Bartholomew; Thomas, and Matthew the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"publican"],"; James",["i","the son"],"of Alphæus, and Lebbæus, whose surname was Thaddæus;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.4","order":"03.03.010.1251"},["b","4"],"Simon the Canaanite, and Judas Iscariot, who also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"betrayed"],"him."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.5","order":"03.03.010.1252"},["b","5"],"These twelve Jesus",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"sent"],"forth, and commanded them, saying, Go not into the way of the Gentiles, and into",["i","any"],"city of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Samaritans"],"enter ye not:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.6","order":"03.03.010.1253"},["b","6"],"But go rather to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"lost"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"sheep"],"of the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.7","order":"03.03.010.1254"},["b","7"],"And as ye go, preach, saying, The kingdom of heaven",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"is at hand"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.8","order":"03.03.010.1255"},["b","8"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Heal"],"the sick, cleanse the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"lepers"],", raise the dead,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"cast out"],"devils:",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"freely"],"ye have received, freely",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_8e"},"give"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.9","order":"03.03.010.1256"},["b","9"],"Provide neither gold, nor silver, nor brass in your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"purses"],","],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.10","order":"03.03.010.1257"},["b","10"],"Nor",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"scrip"],"for",["i","your"],"journey, neither two coats, neither shoes, nor yet staves: for the workman is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"worthy"],"of his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"meat"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.11","order":"03.03.010.1258"},["b","11"],"And into whatsoever city or town ye shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"enter"],", inquire who in it is worthy; and there abide till ye go thence."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.12","order":"03.03.010.1259"},["b","12"],"And when ye come into an house, salute it."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.13","order":"03.03.010.1260"},["b","13"],"And if the house be worthy, let your peace come upon it: but if it be not worthy, let your peace return to you."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.14","order":"03.03.010.1261"},["b","14"],"And whosoever shall not receive you, nor hear your words, when ye depart out of that house or city, shake off the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"dust"],"of your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"feet"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.15","order":"03.03.010.1262"},["b","15"],"Verily I say unto you, It shall be more tolerable for the land of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Sodom"],"and Gomorrha in the day of judgment, than for that city."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.16","order":"03.03.010.1263"},["b","16"],"¶Behold, I send you forth as",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"sheep"],"in the midst of wolves: be ye therefore",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"wise"],"as serpents, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"harmless"],"as doves."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.17","order":"03.03.010.1264"},["b","17"],"But beware of men: for they will deliver you up to the councils, and they will scourge you in their synagogues;"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.18","order":"03.03.010.1265"},["b","18"],"And ye shall be brought before governors and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"kings"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"for my sake"],", for a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"testimony against"],"them and the Gentiles."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.19","order":"03.03.010.1266"},["b","19"],"But when they deliver you up,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"take no thought"],"how or what ye shall speak: for it shall be given you in that same hour what ye shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"speak"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.20","order":"03.03.010.1267"},["b","20"],"For it is not ye that speak, but the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Spirit"],"of your Father which speaketh in you."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.21","order":"03.03.010.1268"},["b","21"],"And the brother shall deliver up the brother to death, and the father the child: and the children shall rise up against",["i","their"],"parents, and cause them to be put to death."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.22","order":"03.03.010.1269"},["b","22"],"And ye shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"hated"],"of all",["i","men"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"for"],"my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"name’s"],"sake: but he that",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_22d"},"endureth"],"to the end shall be saved."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.23","order":"03.03.010.1270"},["b","23"],"But when they persecute you in this city, flee ye into another: for verily I say unto you, Ye shall not have gone over the cities of Israel, till the Son of man be come."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.24","order":"03.03.010.1271"},["b","24"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"disciple"],"is not above",["i","his"],"master, nor the servant above his lord."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.25","order":"03.03.010.1272"},["b","25"],"It is enough for the disciple",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"that he be"],"as his master, and the servant as his lord. If they have called the master of the house Beelzebub, how much more",["i","shall they call"],"them of his household?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.26","order":"03.03.010.1273"},["b","26"],"Fear them not therefore: for there is nothing",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"covered"],", that shall not be revealed; and hid, that shall not be known."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.27","order":"03.03.010.1274"},["b","27"],"What I tell you in darkness,",["i","that"],"speak ye in light: and what ye hear in the ear,",["i","that"],"preach ye upon the housetops."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.28","order":"03.03.010.1275"},["b","28"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"fear not"],"them which kill the body, but are not able to kill the soul: but rather",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"fear"],"him which is able to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"destroy"],"both",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_28d"},"soul"],"and body in",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_28e"},"hell"],"."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.29","order":"03.03.010.1276"},["b","29"],"Are not two",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"sparrows"],"sold for a farthing? and one of them shall not fall on the ground without your Father."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.30","order":"03.03.010.1277"},["b","30"],"But the very",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"hairs"],"of your head are all numbered."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.31","order":"03.03.010.1278"},["b","31"],"Fear ye not therefore, ye are of more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"value"],"than many",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"sparrows"],"."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.32","order":"03.03.010.1279"},["b","32"],"Whosoever therefore shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"confess me"],"before men, him will I confess also before my Father which is in heaven."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.33","order":"03.03.010.1280"},["b","33"],"But whosoever shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"deny"],"me before men, him will I also deny before my Father which is in heaven."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.34","order":"03.03.010.1281"},["b","34"],"Think not that I am come to send",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"peace"],"on earth: I came not to send peace, but a sword."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.35","order":"03.03.010.1282"},["b","35"],"For I am come to set a man at variance against his father, and the daughter against her mother, and the daughter in law against her mother in law."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.36","order":"03.03.010.1283"},["b","36"],"And a man’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"foes"],["i","shall be"],"they of his own",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"household"],"."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.37","order":"03.03.010.1284"},["b","37"],"He that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"loveth"],"father or mother",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_37b"},"more"],"than me is not worthy of me: and he that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_37c"},"loveth"],"son or daughter more than me is not worthy of me."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.38","order":"03.03.010.1285"},["b","38"],"And he that taketh not his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"cross"],", and followeth after me, is not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_38b"},"worthy"],"of me."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.39","order":"03.03.010.1286"},["b","39"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"He"],"that findeth his life shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_39b"},"lose"],"it: and he that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_39c"},"loseth"],"his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_39d"},"life"],"for my sake shall find it."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.40","order":"03.03.010.1287"},["b","40"],"¶He that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"receiveth"],"you",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_40b"},"receiveth"],"me, and he that receiveth me receiveth him that sent me."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.41","order":"03.03.010.1288"},["b","41"],"He that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"receiveth"],"a prophet in the name of a prophet shall receive a prophet’s",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_41b"},"reward"],"; and he that receiveth a righteous man in the name of a righteous man shall receive a righteous man’s reward."],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.42","order":"03.03.010.1289"},["b","42"],"And whosoever shall give to drink unto one of these little ones a cup of cold",["i","water"],"only in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"name"],"of a disciple, verily I say unto you, he shall in no wise",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_42b"},"lose"],"his reward."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.1a","order":"03.03.010.1290"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/12.7.6-7"},"1 Ne. 12:7 (6–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/2.2.1-3"},"Moro. 2:2 (1–3)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/delegation-of-responsibility"},"TG Delegation of Responsibility"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.1b","order":"03.03.010.1292"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostles"},"TG Apostles"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.1c","order":"03.03.010.1294"},["b","1c"],["span.small","GR"],"authority over.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.32"},"D&C 50:32"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/authority"},"TG Authority"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-power-of"},"Jesus Christ, Power of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-power-of"},"Priesthood, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.1d","order":"03.03.010.1296"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/uncleanness"},"Uncleanness"],"."],["div",{"id":"1e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.1e","order":"03.03.010.1298"},["b","1e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heal"},"TG Heal"],"."],["div",{"id":"1f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.1f","order":"03.03.010.1300"},["b","1f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sickness"},"TG Sickness"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.3a","order":"03.03.010.1302"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"tax collector."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.4a","order":"03.03.010.1304"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-betrayal-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Betrayal of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.5a","order":"03.03.010.1306"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.34"},"3 Ne. 28:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.35"},"D&C 107:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.5b","order":"03.03.010.1308"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.52"},"Luke 9:52"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.6a","order":"03.03.010.1310"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.6b","order":"03.03.010.1312"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sheep"},"TG Sheep"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.7a","order":"03.03.010.1314"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"has come."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.8a","order":"03.03.010.1316"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.2"},"Luke 9:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.68"},"D&C 84:68"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.8b","order":"03.03.010.1318"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leprosy"},"TG Leprosy"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.8c","order":"03.03.010.1320"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.67"},"D&C 84:67"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.8d","order":"03.03.010.1322"},["b","8d"],["span.small","GR"],"without payment.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/55.1"},"Isa. 55:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"8e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.8e","order":"03.03.010.1324"},["b","8e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/generosity"},"TG Generosity"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.9a","order":"03.03.010.1326"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/10.4"},"Luke 10:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/22.35.35-36"},"22:35 (35–36)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.18"},"D&C 24:18"],";",["a.scr